title: Border, 1990-84-110, ca. 1955
description: Surrealist scene: composed of varying sized birds, one group of three birds flying, one smaller bird sitting on harp, and another bird in a cage. A large branch, suspended in mid-air, supports the harp and a long flowing drapery, as well as the birdcage. Printed in mauve, black, yellow and white on blue ground.
